name: Cosmic Splash Tee
description:
Blue/Purple Cosmic Splash Tee. 

Perfect for summer!

Hand Made Custom Dyed.

Please bare in mind that every individual tee will look different and unique and not perfectly match the one displayed.

Logo printed on quality 100% cotton t-shirts.

Produced in very limited quantities!

Due to the nature of the dying, hand washing is highly recommended. Every effort is made to strain excess dye out on production, however we cannot take responsibility for dye leakage when washed even though it is highly unlikely!
